                <div class="col s12 m6">
                  <p>Foster parents are often misrepresented in movies and
                    television. At Annie’s Havens we hold ourselves to the highest
                    standards. Licensed by the Ministry of Children and Youth
                    Services, we go above and beyond requirements, and Children’s
                    Aid Societies consistently recognize our homes as some of the
                    best in Ontario.
                  </p>
                  <br />
                  <a
